<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比和贾森在打篮球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不敢相信这已经是儿童中心的最后一天了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这意味着整个夏天都不用上学，也没有儿童中心活动了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他觉得雪莉老师今天一定准备了好玩儿的活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师吹了吹哨子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“脱掉鞋子和袜子吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一幅大大的美国地图摆在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>旁边是几大盘颜料。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大地图是做什么用的？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为了明年的儿童中心，我们要做一张地图挂在墙上装饰体育馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地图会展示出你去过的地方。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，为什么我们要脱掉鞋子和袜子呢？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为你们要印出脚印！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要用脚画画？” 贾森兴奋地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以用脚趾画。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，你们要列出去过的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样才会知道要印在哪里。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去过威斯康星州。” 莉琪边说边写。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我应该去过佛罗里达州。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去过加利福尼亚州！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，密歇根州该怎么写？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124074</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们写完后，就准备画画了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先决定要用什么颜色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一旦跳进颜料盘里，就不能换了。” 雪莉老师提醒他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我选蓝色！” 波比马上说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我选黄色。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我选绿色！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我选紫色！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蓝色颜料在那里！” 雪莉老师对波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“耶！” 波比跳进蓝色颜料盘里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>脚趾在颜料里感觉很凉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！感觉真奇怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，你说得对。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比从宾夕法尼亚州走到加利福尼亚州。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他画出一个贯穿全美国的脚印。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他走向得克萨斯州。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和家人只在得克萨斯州的机场停留过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他觉得那也算。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我做好了，雪莉老师！” 波比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。擦干净脚以后，拿一些闪粉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洒在你们最喜欢的地方。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地图上最喜欢的地方？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，美国你最喜欢的地方。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比边用毛巾擦脚边想。“嗯……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在贾森耳边说了句悄悄话。贾森笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森告诉了莉琪，莉琪告诉了尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他们一起把闪粉洒到同一个地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都最喜欢宾夕法尼亚州吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，因为儿童中心在这里！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且您也在这里，雪莉老师。” 莉琪补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281827</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个夏天，我会想你们的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>